				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/B%E1%BA%A1ch-vi-th%C3%AC-m%E1%BB%99-huy%E1%BB%87n-ti%E1%BB%83u-l%E1%BA%A1i-nh%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%87nh-ngo%E1%BA%A1-n%E1%BB%99i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-khu-ng%C6%B0u-kinh-%C4%91%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%87nh-th%C3%AA-n%E1%BB%99-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-gia/poem-HKs8O_eXeW0NQtrtJLDCXg">Bạch vi thì mộ huyện tiểu lại nhập lệnh ngoạ nội, thường khu ngưu kinh đường hạ lệnh thê nộ tương gia cật trách, Bạch cức dĩ thi tạ vân - 白微時，募縣小吏入令臥內，嘗驅牛經堂下令妻怒將加詰責白亟以詩謝雲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-My-Lu%C3%A2n-giang-b%E1%BA%A1c-m%E1%BB%99-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%83-Ho%C3%A0nh-S%C6%A1n-h%E1%BA%A1/poem-AFPNJSNYG7TnArHK8VgNYw">Độ My Luân giang bạc mộ tương để Hoành Sơn hạ - 渡瀰淪江泊暮將抵橫山下</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Pha-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA/poem-dHKEDEtWvrPZjlKwcmkf2A">Đông Pha tuyệt cú - 東坡絕句</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/Giang-h%E1%BB%93-t%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%ADch-I/poem-r4Olp_bJx0XJrpOG8a1ojg">Giang hồ tự thích (I) - 江湖自適</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tu%E1%BB%87-Trung-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-s%C4%A9/author-vnduJD_TYrIrUDl9fyOqRw">Tuệ Trung thượng sĩ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/H%E1%BA%A1-T%E1%BB%91ng-L%C3%AA-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-tam-ng%E1%BB%B1-s%E1%BB%AD/poem-uKksI8Fd2isrSMjx8B4ytg">Hạ Tống, Lê, Đỗ tam ngự sử - 賀宋黎杜三御使</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/Kim-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ti%C3%AAn-nh%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB-H%C3%A1n-ca-t%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-35Vn44AjbUjdch-9xsSRRg">Kim đồng tiên nhân từ Hán ca tịnh tự - 金銅仙人辭漢歌並序</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-H%E1%BA%A1/author-6YXs2qoM-0pPFaxDDrLTew">Lý Hạ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Nguy%C3%AAn-Ph%E1%BA%A1m/L%C3%BD-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-th%C6%B0-m%E1%BB%87nh-k%E1%BB%B9-ca-ti%E1%BB%85n-h%E1%BB%AFu-t%C3%A1c-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-th%C3%B9/poem-1qGubMaKsUuRNwf0Ze2gRQ">Lý thượng thư mệnh kỹ ca tiễn hữu tác phụng thù - 李尚書命妓歌餞有作奉酬</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-Nguy%C3%AAn-Ph%E1%BA%A1m/author-Twac3f9V9ajA91-vk2CqOQ">Thôi Nguyên Phạm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/Tang-L%E1%BA%A1c-ch%C3%A2u/poem-o3Z9Es__PFbhS6CzEWNF-g">Tang Lạc châu - 桑落洲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Qu%E1%BA%A7n-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc/author-zIVIj-WVByE189TCoytv8g">Lý Quần Ngọc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/Thu-qu%C3%BD-b%E1%BA%A1o-v%C5%A9/poem-tZIZfj_4gkAOAyYCzsfOzQ">Thu quý bạo vũ - 秋季暴雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ho%C3%A0ng-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Th%E1%BB%B1/author-AqEVkg0YBflkFbuAXYlrbA">Hoàng Nguyễn Thự</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Trinh/X%E1%BA%A1-di%C3%AAn-thi/poem-Bk962i4rFoZhD4PLkwDOWw">Xạ diên thi - 射鳶詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Trinh/author-WE75wNuXvrhKJr_UB87GwA">Lưu Trinh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
